name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: addVirtualDevice
desc: Creates a virtual MIDI source

name: bluetoothState
desc: Returns the current Bluetooth state

name: configureBleTransport
desc: Attaches or detaches the BLE implementation.

name: connectToDevice
desc: Connects to the device

name: devices
desc: Gets a list of available MIDI devices and returns it

name: disconnectDevice
desc: Disconnects from the device

name: isNetworkSessionEnabled
desc: Returns the current state of the network session

name: onBluetoothStateChanged
desc: Stream firing events whenever the bluetooth state changes

name: onMidiDataReceived
desc: Stream firing events whenever a midi package is received

name: onMidiDataSent
desc: Stream firing events whenever a midi package is sent

name: onMidiSetupChanged
desc: Stream firing events whenever a change in the MIDI setup occurs

name: removeVirtualDevice
desc:
Removes a previously created virtual MIDI source.
Currently only supported on iOS.

name: sendData
desc: Sends data to the currently connected device

name: setNetworkSessionEnabled
desc: Sets the enabled state of the network session

name: startBluetooth
desc: Starts the Bluetooth subsystem used for BLE MIDI discovery/connection.

name: startScanningForBluetoothDevices
desc: Starts scanning for BLE MIDI devices

name: stopScanningForBluetoothDevices
desc: Stop scanning for BLE MIDI devices

name: teardown
desc: Disconnects from all devices

name: waitUntilBluetoothIsInitialized
desc: Wait for the blueetooth state to be initialized
